apps.title: Learn Next.js Offline [PRO]
apps.description:
Learn Next.js and React for building web apps without compromising performance, user experience, and developer happiness. Develop scalable web apps with Next.js. This Learn Next.js & React app is for web developers who want to improve their React skills by building scalable and maintainable full-stack applications using the modern Next.js web framework. This learn next.js app is designed for complete beginners and No previous coding knowledge is required.
